  <DMS_FlashShock.label>閃光裝置</DMS_FlashShock.label>
  <!-- EN: Activate assault flash array to temporarily blind the incoming enemy, is usually used when facing large  A riot control team can activate them consecutively to fully incapacitate the threatening crowd. After use, it will slowly recharge through its battery. -->
  <DMS_FlashShock.description>啟動突擊閃光陣列暫時致盲來襲的敵人，使用後能透過塔盾手自身的電力緩慢充能。塔盾手小隊在面對大群暴徒能透過小組接連釋放來使威脅人群失能，並同時以鎮暴霰彈槍與電擊棍製服處於恍神狀態的暴徒。</DMS_FlashShock.description>
  
